👹 TROLL 2 – Official Trailer (2025) | Netflix Monster Sequel in 4K
Mountains awaken and legends die blazing. Troll 2 is the explosive new monster adventure streaming on Netflix — Norway’s folklore meets unstoppable destruction.

Film Overview
After the events of the first film, a new, even deadlier troll rises in the Norwegian mountains. Paleontologist Nora and her team—Andreas and Captain Kris—gear up with advanced weapons and ancient mythic secrets to stop destruction from rampaging out of the wild. Norway’s fate won’t wait.
